https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xiLRClQmKSVAbiu6rgCRzNQjcSX.jpg Doraemon, Nobita, Shizuka, Gian, and Suneo set out on an adventure in the Caribbean Sea. Nobita is the captain of a ship and fights his enemies on board. Shizuka gets kidnapped, and a storm impedes their journey. Mini-Dora help Nobita and friends on their journey. When the adventurers finally find the mysterious Treasure Island, they discover it is more than just an ordinary island. Doraemon: Nobita's Treasure Island
